snippet.title: Amber Heard all smiles during hike as Johnny Depp found to be 'wife-beater'
snippet.description:
💖 Please Visit: https://www.facebook.com/Scathc/
💖 Please Subscribe: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCwsKCTW9AItGK_aFz1oMFwg?sub_confirmation=1
✍  Amber Heard put on a smiley display as she headed out for a hike with a friend on Sunday.  The actress, 34, did very little to hide her happiness in photos snapped just hours before Mr Justice Nicol at the High Court ruled that The Sun Newspaper did no wrongdoing in naming her former husband  a 'wife-beater' in an article.  Amber happily stopped and posed for photographers as she got out of her car at the walking destination in Los Angeles and looked in high spirits as she flashed her bright white teeth.  Aquaman star Amber appeared full of joy as she cut a relaxed figure in a red and black chequered shirt teamed with three-quarter length leggins and trainers.  She toted her belongings in a black backpack and tied her hair back in a braid for the long uphill trek with her pal.   The duo looked like they were sharing jokes as they giggled and smiled together as they took in the beautiful surroundings.   On Monday,  has lost his libel battle against News Group Newspapers.   The actor -  ...
💖 #JohnnyDepp, #AmberHeard
